and kill demons.

235
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:33,160
A Soldier is said to be

236
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,740
the sharpest sword of the Yiqi Alliance.

237
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,590
The sword lies hidden in its sheath,

238
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:38,200
and I

239
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:39,750
lie hidden here.

240
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:41,950
I don't need emotions

241
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:43,350
